 Time Complexity
Let:
n = number of crops in crops.txt
 Steps Analysis:
Reading file → O(n)
Searching previous crop → O(n)
Checking all crops for recommendation → O(n)
 Total Time Complexity:
O(n)
✔ Because the program scans the crop list linearly.
 Space Complexity
 Memory Used:
Vector/array to store crop data → O(n)
Few variables (input, flags) → O(1)
 Total Space Complexity:
O(n)
